articles.author: Rod McGuirk, The Associated Press
articles.title: Australia hosts largest-ever Talisman Sabre military exercise - Defense News
articles.description: The event began with live-fire exercises, including Australia’s first use of U.S.-supplied HIMARS rocket systems.
articles.content:
MELBOURNE, Australia The largest-ever war-fighting drills in Australia, Exercise Talisman Sabre, are underway and expected to attract the attention of Chinese spy ships.
